text: dau che neah brahelcha anak( mou ham meat) nung baohbngchaol muoychamnuon nouv avei delke phdal vea hi mk aoy anak haey thveu aoy troung robsa anak mean pheap changaiet daoysaar vea daoy khlachakreng puokke nung niyeay tha hetoaveibeanchea ke min banhchouh kamnbtropy mk aoy keat ryy banhchoun mea la ai kat mneak mk cheamuoy keat? tampit anak kreante chea anak dasatuen promean bonnaoh . haey a l laoh chea anaktheroksaa karpar leu avei teangoasa
